      <title>中国银行提高消费者贷款利率以保护利润率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-banks-increase-consumer-loan-rates-to-protect-margins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国银行削减了低点后仅两周就开始提高消费者贷款利率，这突显了在利润率持续压力的情况下降低资金成本的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-banks-increase-consumer-loan-rates-to-protect-margins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 07:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
