      <title>高盛（Goldman</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/goldman-slashes-s-p-500-target-for-second-time-on-growth-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）策略师本月第二次削减了他们的S＆amp; P 500目标，理由是更高的衰退风险和与关税有关的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/goldman-slashes-s-p-500-target-for-second-time-on-growth-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 06:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲的关税焦虑凹痕市场对防御的乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/europe-s-tariff-angst-dents-market-optimism-on-defense-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲市场上的情绪音乐突然发生了变化，因为对即将到来的关税的担忧超过了德国国防驱动的支出套餐带来的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/europe-s-tariff-angst-dents-market-optimism-on-defense-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 06:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的Lagarde说，保持通货膨胀是一场“持续的战斗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/ecb-s-lagarde-says-keeping-inflation-in-check-constant-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统克里斯汀·拉加尔德（Christine Lagarde）表示，欧洲中央银行无法对通货膨胀持续，因为美国政府的贸易政策造成了不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/ecb-s-lagarde-says-keeping-inflation-in-check-constant-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 06:52:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯顿·马丁（Aston Martin）通过出售股票来筹集更多现金，F1股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/aston-martin-to-raise-125-million-by-selling-shares-f1-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯顿·马丁·拉贡达（Aston Martin Lagonda）全球控股公司（Aston Martin Lagonda Boldings Plc）预计，通过向加拿大亿万富翁劳伦斯·斯特罗尔（Lawrence Stroll）出售更多股票及其在一级方程式赛车队中的少数股权，将筹集至少1.25亿英镑（1.62亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/aston-martin-to-raise-125-million-by-selling-shares-f1-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 06:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
